  "title": "Laravel Webpack Instantsearchjs 2.6.* Reference Errors ",
  "body": "Hi! I have a documentation issue on InstantSearch.js, I could not find what I was looking for which is: \r\nWe ware using Instandsearch.js with Laravel and Webpack.\r\nWe made an update via npm to instantsearch.js 2.6.*.\r\nIf we restart our Laravel Application we get Reference Errors in our JavaScript Files for Example:\r\nReferenceError: $ is not defined in some other JS-Files.\r\nIf we open the Page with the instandsearch we get also this Error:\r\nTypeError: window.instantsearch is not a function\r\n\r\nIf we downgrade to Version Instantsearch.js 2.0.2 everything is working fine.\r\nThats really strange and we have no idea what we can do that version 2.6. is working without these Errors in our other JS-Files.\r\n\r\n",
